lead_paragraph: Brooke McCarty scored 16 points, Joyner Holmes had a double-double and No. 16 Texas opened Big 12 Conference play with a 67-47 win over Texas Tech on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: No. 16 Texas Women Roll Tech 67-47 in Big 12 Opener
